msgstr "3D animirani naslovi"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../titles.rst:178
msgid ""
"Adding a 3D animated title is just as easy, using our **Animated Title** "
"dialog. Use the Title menu (located in the main menu of OpenShot) to launch "
"the Animated Title editor. You can also use the keyboard shortcut "
"**Ctrl+B**. Note: Blender must be installed and configured before this "
"feature will work in OpenShot. See :ref:`blender_install_ref`."
msgstr ""
"Dodavanje 3D animiranog naslova jednako je jednostavno, koristeći naš "
"dijalog **Animirani naslov**. Koristite izbornik Naslov (u glavnom izborniku "
"OpenShota) za pokretanje uređivača animiranih naslova. Također možete "
"koristiti tipkovni prečac **Ctrl+B**. Napomena: Blender mora biti instaliran "
"i konfiguriran prije nego što ova značajka radi u OpenShotu. Pogledajte :ref:"
"`blender_install_ref`."

