# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../titles.rst:261
msgid "Installing Inkscape"
msgstr "Instalacija Inkscapea"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../titles.rst:263
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Advanced Editor` feature in the :guilabel:`Title Editor` "
"dialog requires the latest version of Inkscape (https://inkscape.org/"
"release/) be installed and the OpenShot **Preferences** updated with the "
"correct path to the Inkscape executable. See the :ref:"
"`preferences_general_ref` tab in Preferences."
msgstr ""
"Značajka :guilabel:`Napredni uređivač` u dijalogu :guilabel:`Uređivač "
"naslova` zahtijeva instaliranu najnoviju verziju Inkscapea (https://inkscape."
"org/release/) i ažurirane OpenShot **Postavke** s ispravnom putanjom do "
"Inkscape izvršne datoteke. Pogledajte karticu :ref:`preferences_general_ref` "
"u Postavkama."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../titles.rst:270
msgid "Installing Blender"
msgstr "Instalacija Blendera"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../titles.rst:272
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Animated Title` feature in OpenShot requires the latest "
"version of Blender (https://www.blender.org/download/) be installed and the "
"OpenShot **Preferences** updated with the correct path to the Blender "
"executable. See the :ref:`preferences_general_ref` tab in Preferences. NOTE: "
"The minimum supported version of Blender is 5.0+. Older versions of Blender "
"are not compatible with OpenShot Video Editor."
msgstr ""
"Značajka :guilabel:`Animirani naslov` u OpenShotu zahtijeva instaliranu "
"najnoviju verziju Blendera (https://www.blender.org/download/) i ažurirane "
"OpenShot **Postavke** s ispravnom putanjom do Blender izvršne datoteke. "
"Pogledajte karticu :ref:`preferences_general_ref` u Postavkama. NAPOMENA: "
"Minimalno podržana verzija Blendera je 5.0+. Starije verzije Blendera nisu "
"kompatibilne s OpenShot Video Editorom."

